At your command, I will manage our garrisons or production.  When ordered to 'Manage Garrisons', I will use available training facilities to provide garrisons on systems as required.  If directed to 'Manage Production', I will order our construction yards to produce mines and refineries in order to maximize our production and maintenance capabilities. To issue any of these on-going commands to me, close this message, right-click on my image in the Command Center, and select the appropriate directive from the menu.